<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span>أَخْبَرَنَا الْأَثْرَمُ ,<span class="c5"> عَنْ أَبِي عُبَيْدَةَ:</span> <span class="c3">{يَوْمٌ عَصِيبٌ}</span> <span class="c4">[هود: ٧٧]</span> <span class="c2">«أَيْ شَدِيدٌ , يَعْصِبُ النَّاسَ بِالشَّرِّ»</span> قَالَ:<a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span><span class="c4">[البحر الوافر]</span><a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span>وَكُنْتُ لِزَازَ خَصْمِكَ لَمْ أُعَرِّدْ ... وَقَدْ سَلَكُوكَ فِي يَوْمٍ عَصِيبِ<a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p4"></span><span class="c5">وَقَالَ آخَرُ:</span><a href="#p4" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p5"></span>وَإِنَّكَ إِلَّا تُرْضِ بَكْرَ بْنَ وَائِلٍ ... يَكُنْ لَكَ يَوْمٌ بِالْعِرَاقِ عَصِيبُ<a href="#p5" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p6"></span><span class="c5">وَقَالَ آخَرُ:</span><a href="#p6" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p7"></span>يَوْمٌ عَصِيبٌ يَعْصِبُ الْأَبْطَالَا ... عَصْبَ الْقَوِيِّ السَّلَمَ الطِّوَالَا<a href="#p7" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p8"></span><span class="c5">السَّلَمُ:</span> يَعْنِي الشَّجَرَ<a href="#p8" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>